item.title: SoftLayer_Account_Address
item.description: SoftLayer_Account_Address Service Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Account_Address data type contains information on an address associated with a SoftLayer account. Local accountId Type: integer address1 Line 1 of the address (normally the street address). Type: string address2 Line 2 of the address. Type: string city The city of the address. Type: string contactName The contact name (person, office) of the address.
